<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-10 20:03 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2587 &Cx1f; tta-z
u p BC-GORE-AFL-CIO-930&AMP;ADD-     10-10 1262
</HEADER>
