   I may quibble with Morningstar's underweighting of the most
recent results, but it's giving us an analysis _ at no charge _
that most investors don't have either the time or the experience to
perform.
</P>
<P>
   Harry Domash lives in Aptos, Calif., and publishes the Winning
Investing newsletter. You can read his columns at
www.winninginvesting.com or contact him at
hdomash &LR; winninginvesting.com.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
