   (NYT29) BOSTON -- Oct. 10, 1999 -- BBA-REDSOX-INDIANS-3, 10-10
-- Boston Red Sox base runners Jason Varitek, foreground, and
Darren Lewis coming to home plate and greeted by teammates Jose
Offerman, left, and John Valentin, right, in a five run third
inning for the Sox against the Cleveland Indians during Game 4 of
their playoff series on Sunday. (Jim Davis/Boston Globe Photo)
</P>
